    "level": 2,
    "pages": [
        {
            "text": "Children of wax",
            "pagenum": 0,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_00.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_00.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "Once upon a time, there lived a happy family.",
            "pagenum": 1,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_01.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_01.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "They never fought with each other. They helped their parents at home and in the fields.",
            "pagenum": 2,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_02.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_02.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "But they were not allowed to go near a fire.",
            "pagenum": 3,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_03.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_03.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "They had to do all their work during the night. Because they were made of wax!",
            "pagenum": 4,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_04.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_04.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "But one of the boys longed to go out in the sunlight.",
            "pagenum": 5,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_05.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_05.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "One day the longing was too strong. His brothers warned himâ€¦",
            "pagenum": 6,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_06.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_06.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "But it was too late! He melted in the hot sun.",
            "pagenum": 7,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_07.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_07.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "The wax children were so sad to see their brother melting away.",
            "pagenum": 8,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_08.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_08.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "But they made a plan. They shaped the lump of melted wax into a bird.",
            "pagenum": 9,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_09.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_09.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "They took their bird brother up to a high mountain.",
            "pagenum": 10,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_10.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_10.mp3"
        },
        {
            "text": "And as the sun rose, he flew away singing into the morning light.",
            "pagenum": 11,
            "imageSrc": "/images/0337/0337_11.jpg",
            "audioSrc": "/audio/en/0337/0337_en_11.mp3"
        }
    ]
}